OL,6,FA man barricaded himself into the
OL,7,Fhotel room he was living in and
OL,8,Fstarted a fire, a court has heard.
OL,10,FMichael O'Brien, 48, now of no fixed
OL,11,Fabode, later said he started the blaze
OL,12,Fat The Alexander hotel in Swansea as
OL,13,Fit was the only way to alert people to
OL,14,Fmen "causing trouble" outside his room
OL,15,Fafter police seized his mobile phone
OL,16,Fthe previous day.
OL,18,FProsecutors said other residents at
OL,19,Fthe hotel became aware of smoke coming
OL,20,Funder the door to O'Brien's room in
OL,21,FFebruary this year.
