OL,6,FSwansea Crown Court heard knocks on
OL,7,Fthe door went unanswered and when
OL,8,Fpeople tried to force their way into
OL,9,Fthe room they found O'Brien had
OL,10,Fbarricaded the door.
OL,12,FProsecutor Robin Roach added a number
OL,13,Fof residents forced their way into the
OL,14,Fburning room as they waited for
OL,15,Femergency services to arrive and found
OL,16,Fit was full of "very thick smoke."
OL,18,FO'Brien was arrested at the scene and
OL,19,Fsubsequently gave police a prepared
OL,20,Fstatement.
