OL,6,FIn the statement, he said police had
OL,7,Ftaken his phone and the fire was his
OL,8,Fonly way to draw attention to people
OL,9,Foutside his room.
OL,11,FPolice examined CCTV footage from the
OL,12,Fhotel as part of their investigation
OL,13,Fand found no group of people outside
OL,14,FO'Brien's room, according to the
OL,15,Fprosecutor.
OL,17,FO'Brien previously pleaded guilty to
OL,18,Farson being reckless as to whether
OL,19,Flife was endangered when he appeared
OL,20,Fin the dock for sentencing.
